# Committed deliberately: NEXT_PUBLIC_* is inlined into the browser bundle at
# build time, so this value is public either way. Keeping it here rather than in
# CI config means Cloudflare Workers Builds and GitHub Actions cannot drift apart.
#
# The /api/v1 suffix is required. auth-service registers the console under
# app.Group("/api/v1/platform/auth") and Caddy's `handle /api/v1/platform/*`
# does not strip the prefix, so a bare host here 404s at the gateway.
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.twincord.in/api/v1
